	Equity Distribution to Management



	 


	Since our incorporation, we have raised capital through private sales of our common equity. As of April 14, 2017 we have issued 31,597,572 shares of our common stock to various shareholders, in exchange for cash and services. Specifically, Morten Albrechtsen was issued shares in exchange for cash and Wexotc ApS (a company controlled by Morten Albrecthsen) was issued 1,500,000 for services as a non-executive advisor to the Company. In exchange for these advisory services and $5,000, Mr. Albrechtsen and Wexotec ApS were issued a total of 3,000,000 shares.


	 


	In exchange for the assignment of his pending patent for a prescription sleep remedy, Birger Jan Olsen was issued 18,000,000.


	 




